&lt;td class="lntd">
&lt;pre tabindex="0" class="chroma">&lt;code class="language-cpp" data-lang="cpp">&lt;span class="line">&lt;span class="cl">&lt;span class="err">我们再来看下&lt;/span>&lt;span class="n">QImage类几个常见的构造函数&lt;/span>&lt;span class="err">：&lt;/span>
